                                                527
                                            ],
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "content": " (2 mL). Triethylamine (0.15 mL, 1.08 mmol) is added and the reaction mixture is stirred at room temperature for 17 hrs. The mixture is washed with water (2 mL) then passed through a Telos phase separator. Additional "
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "bbox": [
                                                59,
                                                408,
                                                533,
                                                527
                                            ],
