                                                527
                                            ],
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "content": " (2 mL) is passed through the phase separator. The combined organic layers are concentrated in vacuo to give the crude product. The crude material is purified by preparative HPLC to afford Example 11 (6.0 mg, 5.9%)."
                                        }
